Sweatshop - Bomb/Defuse

de_sweat.bsp

Terrorists: Make your way from the backstreets
into either of the two weapon stashes before the 
Defense canseize your operations. There is a 
delivery parked at each stop, so plant the C4 
at either siteand it should take care 
of any major evidence.

Counter-Terrorists: 

Enter the facility
from the lower parking lot, not far from
where the reported trafficking is taking place.

This is the finalized version of Sweatshop, which I actually ported to CS:GO for fun. I figured it was more optimized and played much better with the new layout changes, so her its is back to Source!

Includes:

  • New environment lighting
  • Assets brought over from the CS:GO version
  • New paths to each bombsite
  • Second Mid is now open
  • Heavy aesthetic changes
  • New custom skybox texture
